ew-shore/" rel="tag">Andrew Shore</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/barnaby-rea/" rel="tag">Barnaby Rea</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/eno/" rel="tag">Eno</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/jakob-lenz/" rel="tag">Jakob Lenz</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/jimmy-holliday/" rel="tag">Jimmy Holliday</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/jonathan-best/" rel="tag">Jonathan Best</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/louise-collett/" rel="tag">Louise Collett</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/rebecca-van-den-berg/" rel="tag">Rebecca van den Berg</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/richard-roberts/" rel="tag">Richard Roberts</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/sigridur-osk/" rel="tag">Sigridur Osk</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/wolfgang-rihm/" rel="tag">Wolfgang Rihm</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Alexa Mason, Alexander Ingram, Andrew Shore, Barnaby Rea, Eno, Jakob Lenz, Jimmy Holliday, Jonathan Best, Louise Collett, Opera lirica, Rebecca van den Berg, Richard Roberts, Sigridur Osk, Wolfgang Rihm"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/6699ffadacad646736fb668601ae4e49" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/soundcloud-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="redazioneGBopera" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="redazione GBopera"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></